title: War and History Audiobooks 1 of 6
description:
A series I put together to give back to other uploaders here and elsewhere on the web.

It's called War and History Audiobooks (although it is mostly about war). I have divided it up into 6 separate torrents because it was about 18 Gigs as one torrent. I have listed the titles here, but since I have already spent a lot of time on this, I have not provided a description. You can look each of them up to get more info if you wish.

This is torrent 1 of 6 containing:

Ancient Greek History
TTC - Rome and the Barbarians
TTC - 1066 (The Conquest) Prof. J Paxton [2012]
Gordon S. Wood - The Radicalism of the American Revolution
Nathaniel Philbrick - Bunker Hill [bobPocket]
Civil War - One Man Great Enough
The 33 Strategies Of War - Audiobook 192kbps - JackDilla


Hope this is satisfactory--let me know if it's not.
I will seed for as long as possible, but give me some help.
